Instantiate DetectCarsYOLO class¶

In [3]:
weights_path = "phase2/YOLO/yolov3.weights" 
# This file is not uploaded to LMS. 
# You can download it from here: https://pjreddie.com/darknet/yolo/
# Make sure that you download thw weights corresponding to YOLOv3-416

config_path = "phase2/YOLO/yolov3.cfg"
labels_path = "phase2/YOLO/coco.names"

detect_yolo = DetectCarsYOLO(weights_path, config_path, labels_path)
